29/12/2006
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- Former Prime Minister Milo Djukanovic confirmed on Thursday (December 28th) that he plans to establish a private university in Montenegro.
Together with two professors, he has established a private company, Universitats, and says he plans to invite foreign lecturers to speak.
Djukanovic left office earlier this year.
(B92, RTRS - 28/12/06)
